    <!-- Legal Notice -->
    <div class="legal-notice">
        <strong>⚖ Legal Notice:</strong>
        By delegating your signature authority, you authorize the delegate to sign
        documents on your behalf during the specified period. All signatures made
        by the delegate will be legally binding and attributed to you. Ensure you
        trust the delegate completely.
    </div>

    <!-- Search Box -->
    <div class="bg-white border mb-4 rounded-3 shadow-sm delegation-search-card" id="delegationcard">
